{"tid":1420748,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4000億!!!!!! 中國人民銀行與香港金融管理局續簽貨幣互換協議","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:45:22.000Z","uid":57076,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7f0aa2fc4546a1119a189733a6ba061211102269","tid":1420748,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"中國人民銀行與香港金融管理局續簽貨幣互換協議<br />\n<br />\n中國人民銀行與香港金融管理局今天公布，已續簽一份為期3年的貨幣互換協議。<br />\n協議規模為4,000億元人民幣，與先前的協議相同，相當於4,700億元港幣。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n香港金融管理局<br />\n2017年11月27日&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n修訂日期: 2017年11月27日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/key-information/press-releases/2017/20171127-3.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fkey-information%2Fpress-releases%2F2017%2F20171127-3.shtml&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnB68f20TVEdZexmFDfnZHo4%3D&h=533bb8e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/key-information/press-releases/2017/20171127-3.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原來2017年已經開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"72212913acb13a39095ae9efd94d6f33e877afe3","tid":1420748,"uid":57076,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:41:07.000Z","msg":"再睇翻呢篇野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「大家好！我係匯豐中國銷售及業務發展部職員！<br />\n<br />\n最近網上流傳中國政府借用香港外匯儲備4000億美元，係真嘅。我哋個CEO都被辭職咗。內部開始滅聲，唔俾我哋再周圍傳，因為驚人擠提。<br />\n<br />\n8月5日港股跌咗700幾點，就係因為班大戶已經收到風，美國知道咗中國政府問香港借錢，同埋中國同伊朗做生意，所以將會提升對中國經濟制裁手段 (3000億10%+匯率操控國)。中國會更加無錢還俾香港，所以大戶及早將資金撤離香港。<br />\n<br />\n大家有股票嘅真係要睇住，大家都知道有香港十年股災週期，上一次係07年，17年無事，專家預計都係呢一兩年嘅事。小心為上，分分鐘渣到無。現金有安全感好多！」"},{"pid":"30fb7a95028fb962b43c188f58624d24a601bc61","tid":1420748,"uid":57076,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:45:12.000Z","msg":"人民幣國際化，其中一個手段係推高左人民幣個匯率，然後比離岸人民幣慢慢跌<br />\n<br />\n中國印銀紙同我地換，姐係我地香港金管局接緊一批貶值既廢紙咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ecfc038cb53a35d989bc2cd0dfeead08e95c13","tid":1420748,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336c459a959968df5794b38db352ed8236dcef98","tid":1420748,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae6bb174fd1f533c7b3e6a4d3bafcdb8a799bab","tid":1420748,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港已被一鋪清袋</span></span>"},{"pid":"6f96c15e06949ec0d638195dd00fbf6ea930beba","tid":1420748,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eae6bb174fd1f533c7b3e6a4d3bafcdb8a799bab","tid":1420748,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港已被一鋪清袋</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:50:37.000Z","msg":"焦土<br />\n我要攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2abf520fe833c8b9f83c59656073b3fc149feb2","tid":1420748,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:52:11.000Z","msg":"財政部本周四在香港招標發行50億元人民幣國債<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港電台-財經2019年6月17日 下午3:53 <br />\n<br />\n國家財政部表示，今年將在境外發行150億元人民幣國債，當中50億元將於本周四在香港招標發行，下周一交收。<br />\n其中35億元為兩年期國債，另有10億元的5年期國債，可供合資格的中央結算系統(CMU)成員競價投標，每半年派息一次。<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波表示，特區政府歡迎財政部連續11年在香港發行人民幣國債，充分體現中央政府支持鞏固香港作為全球離岸人民幣業務樞紐的地位，有助推動香港債券市場發展。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%E6%9C%AC%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%8B%9B%E6%A8%99%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C50%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5-075322466.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258B%259B%25E6%25A8%2599%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A1%258C50%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2582%25B5-075322466.html&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnB68f20TVEdZexmFDfnZHo4%3D&h=ef10529f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%E6%9C%AC%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%8B%9B%E6%A8%99%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C50%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5-075322466.html</a>"},{"pid":"262aeda594aac65decbc41672cbde24388f5210c","tid":1420748,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:54:28.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"38ee41b7b8e19ae7a27ce2a0a5aedc27733a9fe7","tid":1420748,"uid":46314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ae8fc7fbff01891efc892e664c26204591660118","tid":1420748,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:54:41.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"baa446972455639a2c1b513a254de3633c567cbf","tid":1420748,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"3a34372bc064c65c5c8d8791d1a892be34809ce0","tid":1420748,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:55:04.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"0dc9716228be57586661887e113dbea0a568f74c","tid":1420748,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:55:17.000Z","msg":"5"},{